window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Expansion pack unlocked! It's time to level up in a brave new world!&nbsp;</p> <p>When Sam's unique superpower that lets him level up like a video game character unlocks a new, higher-level world, he and his team of gorgeous superheroines will find themselves challenged by the great, looming evil that lives there.</p> <p>Worse, if Sam can’t level up enough, gather up a strong enough party, and finish enough quests, well, let’s just say that it won’t just be this new world that gets destroyed, but Earth as well!&nbsp;</p> <p>Thankfully, this new world will unlock new powers, new game systems, and new loot, as well as new beautiful and powerful women to romance. And dragons. That is all.&nbsp;</p> <p>This book contains space-hopping super powers, fantastic magic, more beautiful women, intriguing new game systems, cool dragons, a brand new world, and the ability to become the strongest person the universe has ever seen. That’s right, we said universe.</p>"; 
